Vite Install and Setup

    - Open terminal
    - Install Vite latest version

      npm create vite@latest

      There are different method to create a vite using

        - npm
        - yarn
        - pnpm

    - Type your Project Name
    - Select a Framework (any one)

        - Vanilla (Selected)
        - Vue
        - React
        - Preact
        - Lit
        - Svelte
        - Solid
        - Qwik
        - Others

    - Select a Varient 

        - TypeScript
        - JavaScript (Selected)

    Application run

        cd project Name
        npm Install
        npm run dev

Entry Point:

        index.html

